msgid "# De Morgan's Law for Finsets\n"
"\n"
"Remember set difference from Level 3? В§0 contains elements in В§1\n"
"but not in В§2, with В§3.\n"
"\n"
"Now you'll prove a fundamental identity connecting set difference with\n"
"union and intersection вҖ” **De Morgan's law for sets**:\n"
"\n"
"В§4\n"
