"wrapped in the common В§13 hypothesis.\n"
"\n"
"**New move**: To prove a negation like В§14 (which is В§15),\n"
"use В§16 to assume membership, then derive a contradiction using\n"
"В§17 (where В§18) and В§19 or В§20.\n"
"\n"
"**Nested projections**: In the backward direction, you'll encounter a\n"
"nested conjunction В§21. You can\n"
"chain В§22/В§23 projections to reach any component:\n"
"- В§24 (first component of the first conjunct)\n"
"- В§25 (second component of the first conjunct)\n"
"- В§26 (first component of the second conjunct)\n"
"- В§27 (second component of the second conjunct)\n"
