#: Game.Levels.Fintype.L08_SubtypeCounting
msgid "# Subtypes of Finite Types\n"
"\n"
"You've been using В§0 since the first world. But what IS В§1?\n"
"It's a **subtype**: В§2 вҖ” the natural numbers\n"
"less than В§3. Even though В§4 is infinite, the predicate В§5 picks\n"
"out only finitely many values.\n"
"\n"
"More generally, В§6 picks out the elements of В§7\n"
"satisfying the predicate В§8. When В§9 is finite, any subtype is\n"
"automatically finite too вҖ” Lean synthesizes the В§10 instance\n"
"without you having to construct it.\n"
"\n"
"The composition rules you've learned (products multiply, sums add,\n"
"functions exponentiate) have a companion for subtypes:\n"
"\n"
"В§11\n"
"\n"
"The theorem В§12 captures this: the count of\n"
"elements NOT satisfying В§13 equals the total minus those satisfying В§14.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Given that В§15 has 10 elements and 3 satisfy В§16,\n"
"prove that 7 do not."
msgstr ""

