#: Game.Levels.PsetCardinality
msgid "# Problem Set: Cardinality and Counting\n"
"\n"
"You've completed four worlds of counting theory:\n"
"- **Cardinality**: the card_* lemma family вҖ” empty, singleton,\n"
"  insert, erase, subset, union, intersection, complement, product\n"
"- **Abstraction Ladder**: List вҶ’ Multiset вҶ’ Finset, permutations,\n"
"  nodup, toFinset, and the card/length bridge\n"
"- **Fintype**: counting elements of types вҖ” products, sums,\n"
"  functions, subtypes, equivalences\n"
"- **Counting Types**: concrete computations with binary strings,\n"
"  grid labelings, falling factorials, and embeddings\n"
"\n"
"Now apply these skills to **fresh problems** with sparser hints.\n"
"No new definitions вҖ” only retrieval and transfer of taught moves."
