"В§0\n"
"\n"
"**Why multiply by 2?** The standard formula is\n"
"В§1. In natural numbers, division\n"
"is floor division: В§2, not В§3. If В§4 happened to\n"
"be odd (it can't, but Lean doesn't know that without proof), dividing\n"
