"pairs, so В§11. This is the **fold-and-add** or\n"
"**pairing** argument. The factor of 2 in our statement comes\n"
"directly from writing the sum twice.\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, this pairing can be expressed via В§12,\n"
"which reverses the indexing of a sum. The algebraic proof you wrote\n"
"captures the same content through induction вҖ” both approaches\n"
"ultimately rely on the symmetry В§13.\n"
"\n"
"**Key move**: В§14 distributes В§15 into В§16,\n"
"letting you isolate В§17 for the IH. Without this step, В§18\n"
"can't see where to apply the IH because it's buried inside a product.\n"
