"the card facts, then close with В§2. You'll use this pattern\n"
"throughout the problem set.\n"
"\n"
"**Your first task**: Given two finsets В§3 and В§4 with known sizes\n"
"and known overlap, and an element В§5 that belongs to В§6,\n"
