"an *arbitrary finset* В§0 using В§1. The base case was\n"
"В§2 and the step was В§3.\n"
"\n"
"In this world, you'll prove **classical summation formulas** вҖ” identities\n"
"about В§4 вҖ” using a different pattern: **natural\n"
