"\n"
"This is the tuple base case вҖ” analogous to the empty list В§3.\n"
"Every inductive argument about tuples starts here.\n"
"\n"
"The fact that В§4 is empty also means something powerful:\n"
"*any* statement about all elements of В§5 is vacuously true.\n"
"In Lean, В§6 proves anything when В§7, because\n"
"no such В§8 can ever exist.\n"
"\n"
