#: Game.Levels.FinTuples.L14_TuplesAsData
msgid "# Tuples Represent Real Data\n"
"\n"
"So far, every exercise has been about structural properties of\n"
"tuples: how В§0 and В§1 relate, how В§2 proves equality.\n"
"Now you'll see tuples used as **data** вҖ” specifically, as vectors\n"
"whose entries you can compute with.\n"
"\n"
"The tuple В§3 can represent a 2D vector. The tuple\n"
"В§4 is another. Their **componentwise sum** вҖ” adding\n"
"corresponding entries вҖ” should give В§5:\n"
"\n"
"| Index | В§6 | В§7 | Sum |\n"
"|---|---|---|---|\n"
"| 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 |\n"
"| 1 | 0 | 3 | 3 |\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, componentwise sum is expressed as a function:\n"
