"**Note**: Bare В§11 (without В§12) is now available, and it will work\n"
"on some goals. But В§13 is the skill being taught here вҖ” it gives\n"
"you control over exactly which lemmas are applied, which makes proofs\n"
"more readable and maintainable.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: An element В§14 is in В§15. Prove\n"
"that В§16.\n"
"\n"
"Use В§17 to unfold the union and concrete memberships in В§18\n"
"in one step, then close with В§19."
