#: Game.Levels.Powerset.L12_CardPowerset
msgid "Three steps: В§0, В§1, В§2.\n"
"\n"
"The В§3 brings В§4 into the context. Then В§5\n"
"substitutes the known card value. Finally В§6 closes the goal\n"
"because Lean computes В§7 automatically.\n"
"\n"
"**A useful table**:\n"
"| Elements (В§8) | Subsets (В§9) |\n"
"|:-:|:-:|\n"
"| 0 | 1 |\n"
"| 1 | 2 |\n"
"| 2 | 4 |\n"
"| 3 | 8 |\n"
"| 4 | 16 |\n"
"| 5 | 32 |\n"
"\n"
"This exponential growth is why brute-force subset enumeration\n"
"quickly becomes impractical вҖ” and why we need structural results\n"
"like the binomial coefficient to count subsets of a specific size.\n"
"\n"
"**Shortcut**: You can also do this in one step with\n"
