"Here's everything in your toolkit:\n"
"\n"
"**Construction**: В§0, В§1, В§2, В§3, В§4\n"
"\n"
"**Extraction**: В§5, В§6, В§7, В§8, В§9\n"
"\n"
"**Equality**: В§10 (for Fin or functions), В§11, В§12\n"
"\n"
"**Inequality**: В§13 (literals), В§14 (general)\n"
