"is В§21 вҖ” but why should 2 come first? The set of elements\n"
"in a group with order dividing 6 has no canonical indexing. These\n"
"are collections defined by a **membership predicate** (В§22 if\n"
"В§23), not by position.\n"
"\n"
"Phase 2 introduces В§24 вҖ” unordered finite collections with\n"
"decidable membership вҖ” to handle exactly this. You'll build finite\n"
"sets, prove membership facts, and compute with set operations. The\n"
