#: Game.Levels.FinsetOperations.L05_Subset
msgid "The pattern for subset proofs:\n"
"1. В§0 вҖ” unfolds В§1 to В§2\n"
"2. В§3 вҖ” introduce an element and its membership in В§4\n"
"3. В§5 вҖ” unfold what В§6 could be\n"
"4. В§7 вҖ” handle each possibility\n"
"5. In each case: substitute and prove membership in В§8\n"
"\n"
"This is an **element-chasing** proof: you take an arbitrary element of\n"
"В§9 and show it must be in В§10. The case analysis on В§11 ensures you\n"
"consider every element of В§12.\n"
"\n"
"In plain mathematics: to show В§13, take any В§14 and\n"
"show В§15.\n"
"\n"
"The subset relation В§16 is a **partial order** вҖ” it satisfies\n"
"three properties:\n"
"- **Reflexivity**: В§17 (every set is a subset of itself вҖ”\n"
"  В§18)\n"
"- **Transitivity**: if В§19 and В§20, then\n"
"  В§21 (chain the element-chasing: any В§22 is in В§23\n"
"  by the first, then in В§24 by the second)\n"
"- **Antisymmetry**: if В§25 and В§26, then В§27\n"
"  (you'll see this in Level 7 as В§28)\n"
"\n"
"These three properties make finsets with В§29 a **partially ordered\n"
"set** вҖ” a structure you'll study in depth in the orders and lattices course."
