msgid "Congratulations! You proved a non-trivial sum identity entirely by\n"
"finset induction.\n"
"\n"
"**The identity**:\n"
"В§0\n"
"\n"
"**Your proof used every tool from this world**:\n"
"1. В§1 вҖ” the induction principle\n"
"2. В§2 вҖ” peeling sums over В§3\n"
"3. В§4 вҖ” peeling cardinality\n"
"4. The induction hypothesis вҖ” linking В§5 to В§6\n"
"5. В§7 вҖ” closing the algebra\n"
"\n"
"This is the **collect-and-close** strategy in its complete form:\n"
"collect all the pieces by rewriting (peel lemmas + IH), then close\n"
"the resulting arithmetic mechanically. The mathematical thinking is\n"
"in recognizing which quantities need peeling and choosing the right\n"
"lemmas вҖ” the algebra is left to В§8.\n"
"\n"
"**Looking ahead**: The SummationFormulas world applies a variant of\n"
"this pattern вҖ” natural number induction combined with\n"
"В§9 вҖ” to prove classical formulas like the Gauss sum,\n"
"geometric sums, and the sum of odd numbers."
