#: Game.Levels.AbstractionLadder.L20_PrimeFactorsGrounding
msgid "# The Ladder in Mathematics: Prime Factorization\n"
"\n"
"So far, the lists in this world have been abstract: В§0 or\n"
"В§1. But the abstraction ladder captures real mathematical\n"
"distinctions. Consider the prime factorization of 12:\n"
"\n"
"В§2\n"
"\n"
"The factorization can be represented at each layer:\n"
"\n"
"| Layer | Representation | What it captures |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| **List** | В§3 | An ordered sequence of prime factors |\n"
"| **Multiset** | В§4 | The prime factorization (multiplicity matters) |\n"
"| **Finset** | В§5 | The set of prime divisors |\n"
"\n"
"Each layer answers a different question:\n"
