#: Game.Levels.BinomialCoefficients.L07_DerivingChooseSelf
msgid "# Deriving В§0 from Symmetry\n"
"\n"
"In Level 1, we gave you В§1 (В§2) as a fact.\n"
"But now that you have **symmetry**, you can *derive* it!\n"
"\n"
"The key insight: the two boundary values aren't independent.\n"
