"\n"
"Choosing all В§4 items is the same as leaving out В§5 items, which\n"
"gives В§6.\n"
"\n"
"## New tool: Backward rewrite\n"
"\n"
"You know В§7 rewrites the **left** side of В§8 to the right side.\n"
"Sometimes you need the reverse: В§9 (written В§10)\n"
"rewrites the **right** side to the left side.\n"
"\n"
"For example, if В§11, then:\n"
"- В§12 replaces В§13 with В§14 in the goal\n"
