#: Game.Levels.FinsetOperations.L13_IntersectionCommutativity
msgid "# Proving a Set Identity with ext\n"
"\n"
"Now you'll prove **intersection commutativity**: В§0.\n"
"The proof uses В§1/В§2 and В§3 from Level 9 to swap the conjunction\n"
"components in both directions.\n"
"\n"
"**A note on notation**: Finset В§4 and В§5 are actually lattice\n"
"operations В§6 and В§7 under the hood. You may occasionally see В§8 or\n"
"В§9 in the infoview. This is just an alternative notation вҖ” the\n"
"membership lemmas (В§10, В§11) work the same way.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that В§12."
msgstr ""

