#: Game.Levels.MeetFin.L13_EmptyType
msgid "# Fin 0 Has No Elements\n"
"\n"
"What is В§0? It's the type of natural numbers less than 0.\n"
"But no natural number is less than 0, so **В§1 is empty**.\n"
"\n"
"This means: if you ever have В§2 in your context, you have\n"
"a contradiction. From a contradiction, you can prove anything вҖ”\n"
"including В§3.\n"
"\n"
"The key insight: В§4 gives a proof of В§5, but no\n"
"natural number satisfies this. So В§6 can derive В§7 from\n"
"the contradictory hypothesis.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Given В§8, prove В§9.\n"
"\n"
"Strategy: extract the impossible bound with В§10,\n"
"then close with В§11."
msgstr ""

