#: Game.Levels.BinomialCoefficients.L10_AbsorptionIdentity
msgid "В§0 states that\n"
"В§1.\n"
"\n"
"This is the **absorption identity**. It connects adjacent entries\n"
"in Pascal's triangle through multiplication.\n"
"\n"
"## Syntax\n"
"В§2\n"
"\n"
"## Combinatorial meaning\n"
"Choosing a В§3-member committee from В§4 people and then\n"
"picking a chair (right side) equals picking the chair first from\n"
"В§5 people and then choosing the remaining В§6 members (left side).\n"
"\n"
"## Related\n"
"This can be derived from the factorial formula\n"
"В§7."
msgstr ""

