"**intermediate list** that connects them вҖ” a list reachable from\n"
"В§1 by one swap AND from which В§2 is reachable\n"
"by one swap.\n"
"\n"
"**How to find the intermediate**: Look at the first element.\n"
"The source starts with В§3, the target starts with В§4. You need\n"
"В§5 at the front eventually. Try keeping В§6 at the front for the\n"
"first swap (rearrange the tail), then swap В§7 and В§8 in the\n"
