#: Game.Levels.MeetFin.L19_ModularArithmetic
msgid "# Enrichment: Fin Has Arithmetic\n"
"\n"
"*This level is an enrichment aside вҖ” a mathematical surprise that\n"
"connects В§0 to a different area of mathematics. The main course\n"
"path resumes in the next level.*\n"
"\n"
"You've been treating В§1 as an index set вҖ” a collection of\n"
"positions В§2. But В§3 also supports **arithmetic**,\n"
"and it works differently from natural number arithmetic.\n"
"\n"
"What is В§4 in В§5? On natural numbers, it's В§6. But В§7\n"
"only has elements В§8 вҖ” there is no В§9. Addition on\n"
"В§10 **wraps around**: it takes the result modulo В§11.\n"
"\n"
"So В§12 because В§13.\n"
"This is **modular arithmetic** вҖ” the arithmetic of clocks, cyclic\n"
"groups, and the integers mod В§14.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Find two elements В§15 such that\n"
"В§16 (their sum wraps around to zero) and their natural\n"
"number values sum to В§17.\n"
"\n"
"(Hint: on a 5-hour clock, which two different hours are diametrically\n"
"opposite вҖ” summing to a full rotation?)"
msgstr ""

