msgid "# The Factorial as a Product\n"
"\n"
"In the previous level, you computed a specific factorial value using\n"
"the recursive definition. Now you'll prove the general connection\n"
"between the factorial and big-operator products:\n"
"\n"
"В§0\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove this product-to-factorial connection by induction,\n"
"using В§1/В§2 (from the constant-product level)\n"
"and В§3/В§4 (from the previous level).\n"
"\n"
"**Note**: In Level 10, В§5 was disabled to force you to unfold the\n"
"factorial step by step. Here, В§6 is available again вҖ” the base case\n"
"В§7 is definitionally true, and you've already learned the\n"
"recursive structure."
msgstr ""

