#: Game.Levels.FinTuples.L20_ReconstructionStrategy
msgid "# The Reconstruction Strategy\n"
"\n"
"In Level 18, you proved a tuple equals В§0 by checking\n"
"each index. There's a second strategy: **reconstruct**\n"
"the tuple from its head and tail using В§1.\n"
"\n"
"Given information about the head (В§2) and tail (В§3)\n"
"of a tuple, you can determine the full tuple:\n"
"\n"
"1. В§4 вҖ” this gives\n"
"   В§5\n"
"2. В§6 вҖ” substitute known values to get\n"
"   В§7 (which is В§8)\n"
"3. В§9 вҖ” close the goal\n"
"\n"
"You practiced В§10 in Level 19 вҖ” flipping equations to get the\n"
"direction you need. Here you'll combine В§11 with В§12\n"
"to substitute known values into the reconstruction identity.\n"
"\n"
"This is a different proof technique from the В§13 + case split\n"
"approach. Both work вҖ” the reconstruction approach is often shorter.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Reconstruct В§14 from its head and tail."
msgstr ""

