msgid "Congratulations вҖ” you've completed **Finset Operations**!\n"
"\n"
"You proved De Morgan's second law for sets:\n"
"В§0.\n"
"\n"
"The forward direction required the most sophisticated use of\n"
"В§1 yet: you assumed the *entire disjunction* was false,\n"
"then showed this forces both В§2 and В§3, contradicting\n"
"the negated conjunction. Each component (В§4, В§5) was\n"
"itself proven by contradiction вҖ” a nested use of В§6.\n"
"\n"
"Together with Level 17 (De Morgan's first law), you've proven both\n"
"De Morgan laws for sets:\n"
"- В§7\n"
"- В§8\n"
"\n"
"These mirror the propositional De Morgan laws:\n"
"- В§9\n"
"- В§10\n"
"\n"
"Your finset operations toolkit:\n"
"\n"
"| Operation | Membership lemma | Logic form |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| В§11 | В§12 | В§13 |\n"
"| В§14 | В§15 | В§16 |\n"
"| В§17 | В§18 | В§19 |\n"
"| В§20 | В§21 | В§22 |\n"
"| В§23 | В§24 | В§25 |\n"
"| В§26 | В§27 / В§28 | В§29 |\n"
"\n"
"The proof recipe for any set identity:\n"
"1. В§30 вҖ” reduce to element-wise logic\n"
"2. В§31 вҖ” unfold all operations\n"
"3. Handle the resulting вҲ§/вҲЁ/В¬ with В§32, В§33, В§34/В§35\n"
"4. When stuck on extracting positive from negative: В§36\n"
"\n"
"**The bigger picture**: Across this world, you've proved the key\n"
"axioms of a **distributive lattice with difference**:\n"
"\n"
"| Property | Level | Statement |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Idempotency | L09, L12 | В§37, В§38 |\n"
"| Commutativity | L13, L14 | В§39, В§40 |\n"
"| Associativity | L15 | В§41 |\n"
"| Identity | L10 | В§42 |\n"
"| Absorption | L22 | В§43 |\n"
"| Distributivity | L23, L24 | both directions |\n"
"| De Morgan | L18, L25 | both laws |\n"
"\n"
"To get a full **Boolean algebra**, you'd also need a complement\n"
"operation (В§44) and complement laws (В§45,\n"
"В§46). Finsets don't have a natural complement вҖ”\n"
"that requires a universal set В§47, which you'll meet in the\n"
"Cardinality world as В§48. For now, set difference\n"
"(В§49) plays the role of a relative complement.\n"
"\n"
"**What's next**: The next world covers В§50 вҖ” applying a\n"
"function to every element of a finset, and the relationship between\n"
"injectivity and cardinality of images."
msgstr ""

