#: Game.Levels.BinomialCoefficients.L10_AbsorptionIdentity
msgid "# The Absorption Identity\n"
"\n"
"The factorial formula from Level 8 isn't just a curiosity вҖ” it\n"
"implies one of the most important binomial coefficient identities:\n"
"\n"
"В§0\n"
"\n"
"This is the **absorption identity**. It has a beautiful combinatorial\n"
"interpretation called the **committee chair** argument:\n"
"\n"
"- **Right side**: Choose a В§1-member committee from В§2 people,\n"
"  then pick one of the В§3 members to be chair.\n"
"- **Left side**: Pick the chair first (В§4 choices), then choose\n"
"  the remaining В§5 committee members from the other В§6 people.\n"
"\n"
"Both sides count the same thing вҖ” the number of ways to form a\n"
"committee with a designated chair вҖ” so they must be equal.\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, this is В§7:\n"
"В§8\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Apply the absorption identity for В§9."
msgstr ""

