msgid "# The Dual Separation Fact\n"
"\n"
"In Level 7, you proved that В§0 images never equal\n"
"В§1 вҖ” the **castSucc/last separation**.\n"
"\n"
"Here is the dual: В§2 images never equal В§3 вҖ” the\n"
