"| Prove В§28 inequality | В§29 | Level 21 |\n"
"| Existential witness | В§30 | Level 22 |\n"
"\n"
"**Where this is going**: В§31 is the *canonical* finite type in\n"
"Lean вҖ” the standard model that everything connects back to. Every\n"
"finite type with В§32 elements is equivalent to В§33, making it\n"
"the universal representative. A function В§34 is essentially\n"
"an В§35-tuple: an ordered list of В§36 elements from В§37. You'll\n"
"explore this idea in the FinTuples world.\n"
"\n"
"Beyond tuples, you'll meet В§38 (unordered finite collections),\n"
"В§39 (types with finitely many elements), and big operators\n"
"like В§40 and В§41 over finite index sets. All of these are built on\n"
"the foundation you've just learned.\n"
"\n"
"(As you saw in Level 19, В§42 also carries modular arithmetic вҖ”\n"
