"\n"
"The **intersection** В§0 contains only the elements that belong to\n"
"*both* В§1 and В§2. The membership characterization is:\n"
"\n"
"В§3\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, this is В§4:\n"
"В§5\n"
"\n"
"The proof move: В§6 converts an intersection\n"
"membership goal into a conjunction. Then you use В§7 to split\n"
"the conjunction into two goals (membership in В§8 and membership in В§9),\n"
"and prove each one separately.\n"
"\n"
