msgid "You've proved the **partition identity**: В§0.\n"
"\n"
"Every finset В§1 decomposes into exactly two pieces relative to В§2:\n"
"- Elements in В§3 but not in В§4 (the set difference)\n"
"- Elements in both В§5 and В§6 (the intersection)\n"
