"This is exactly В§12, which you'll\n"
"use in the Cardinality world for **complement counting**. Now you\n"
"know *why* complement counting works вҖ” it follows from this\n"
"partition identity.\n"
"\n"
"Note: This level used В§13 for the first time in this world.\n"
"В§14 creates two subgoals: one where В§15\n"
"and one where В§16. It's the tool for deciding which side\n"
"of a disjunction to prove when the deciding condition is a proposition."
