#: Game.Levels.BigOpAlgebra.L14_CalcBlocks
msgid "# calc Blocks: Multi-Step Equality Proofs\n"
"\n"
"When a proof requires several rewrites in sequence, writing them\n"
"as individual В§0 steps works but obscures the logical flow.\n"
"The В§1 tactic organizes multi-step equalities into a readable\n"
"chain:\n"
"\n"
"В§2\n"
"\n"
"Each line proves one step of the chain. The В§3 refers to the\n"
"right-hand side of the previous line. Lean checks that the chain\n"
"connects: the first expression on the left, through each\n"
"intermediate step, to the final expression.\n"
"\n"
"**Key syntax rules**:\n"
"- The first line names the starting expression\n"
"- Each subsequent line starts with В§4 (the underscore is mandatory)\n"
"- Each В§5 opens tactic mode for that step\n"
"- You can also use term proofs: В§6.\n"
"  This is shorthand for В§7 вҖ” the\n"
"  lemma directly proves the equality without entering tactic mode.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that В§8 using a\n"
"calc chain. The proof has two natural steps:\n"
"1. Split В§9 into В§10 using В§11\n"
"2. Substitute the known value of В§12\n"
"\n"
"**Alternative**: You can also solve this with chained В§13 if you\n"
"prefer the compact style. Both approaches are valid."
msgstr ""

