#: Game.Levels.CountingTypes.L07_FactorialConnection
msgid "В§0\n"
"\n"
"The theorem В§1 captures this identity directly.\n"
"In Level 6, you proved В§2 by manual\n"
"unfolding вҖ” now you have the general shortcut.\n"
"\n"
"This connects two counting perspectives:\n"
"\n"
"| Notation | Meaning | Lean |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| В§3 | ordered selections of В§4 from В§5 | В§6 |\n"
"| В§7 | orderings of all В§8 items | В§9 |\n"
"| В§10 | selecting all = ordering all | В§11 |\n"
"\n"
"**Looking ahead**: The binomial coefficient В§12 divides\n"
"the falling factorial by В§13 to remove the ordering:\n"
"В§14. Having both В§15\n"
"and В§16 as formal objects makes this definition precise."
msgstr ""

